<h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What Problem Does This Solve?</h2>
<p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6;">You want a soft, huggable companion that feels premium but costs less than mainstream branded plushes. You're tired of stiff, cheaply-made stuffed animals. You need a gift that's genuinely thoughtful—not mass-produced plastic. Or maybe you just want something cute and cozy to cuddle during movie nights or lonely winter evenings. Enter the Fluffy Rabbit Plush Toy.</p>

