    <div style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">Step 1: Unpack and Fluff</div>
    <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.5;">Remove the plush from its packaging. Gently squeeze, knead, and cuddle it to restore its fluffy shape. If it arrived slightly compressed from shipping, gentle manipulation within the first 24 hours will bring out its full softness and volume. The plush material is designed to bounce back.</p>
