  <div style="padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--muted); border-radius: var(--radius);">
    <div style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">Step 2: Spot Clean Only (Never Machine Wash)</div>
    <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.5;">Do not machine wash. For minor stains or dirt, use a damp cloth with mild soap and gently dab the affected area. Allow to air dry completely. For more stubborn stains, consult spot-cleaning guides designed for delicate fabrics. Machine washing will damage the seams and plush material.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--muted); border-radius: var(--radius);">
